&quot;Bah...that never worked...stupid parlor tricks...&quot;<br>
<br>
Urda instead opened her cloak and watched the sun creep below the horizon.  She's on her way to Kithicor by now.  She best camp before trekking across.<br>
<br>
Knowing the opposite was likely the case, Urda summoned her wolf spirit.<br>
<br>
&quot;Wora is out by Kithicor's edge.  Go and protect her.  Now!&quot;<br>
<br>
The wolf spirit made no motion except to immediately begin running off into the distance.  She doubted he would make it in time to stop her.  But he might be able to defend her.<br>
